role_dependencies: Installs Java on nearly any OS
Ensures Snap is installed on Linux systems
role_description: An Ansible role that handles the connection process for hosts that have not been reassigned a "secure" \ non-default port and sets variables that are used later in the playbook
role_description_full_overview: This role is intended to be used as the first role in the playbook.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that handles the connection process for hosts that have not been reassigned a "secure" \ non-default port and sets variables that are used later in the playbook.
